{"tid":1407400,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屋企個藍絲老母仲喺度屌聽日罷工阻到佢","createTime":"2019-08-04T15:20:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T21:37:29.000Z","uid":278994,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9a2c8defc539da70ddc3f17e9bfade733581d1bf","tid":1407400,"uid":278994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:20:44.000Z","msg":"話說屋企個<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">藍絲</span></span>老母睇新聞見到聽日不合作運動，就屌人罷工阻佢返工係死仆街。<br />\n我地串佢咁撚中意返工你做咩打8號風球唔返工<br />\n你做咩放假？比我地串親就一句「<span style=\"color: blue;\">我打8號風返唔返工關你地咩事？</span>」撻落嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n前線班後生仔幫你擋子彈，你返少一日工係唔係會死<br />\n佢可以咁冇人性咁講：「<span style=\"color: red;\">我洗乜幫佢<span style=\"color: red;\"></span>地擋子彈，佢地想死係佢地嘅事」</span><br />\n佢講講下愈講愈on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲話班狗先咁EQ高 先忍我地咁耐冇打死人喎 如果係維尼早就出老解喎人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢講完呢句 我地三個真係爆笑左出嚟<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">重點嚟喇！</span></span>佢仲話佢班on9大陸鄉下朋友話 中國隊對香港隊打ice hockey係大陸特登輸 之後就打交嚟打死香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n笑到我地三個仆晒街 咁嘅打飛機言論都真係得佢同班大陸朋友先講得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見到我地三個恥笑佢 就惱羞郁手打人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見到佢呢個on9樣我地真係冇眼睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有個咁唔生性嘅老母 我地三個想比啲教訓佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想佢試下比黑警冇差別扑頭 食下放題催淚彈咁<br />\n有冇咩方法？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"414716d081dda1a6d2155b8c4d53fc561548a25b","tid":1407400,"uid":296166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T16:05:33.000Z","msg":"完全明白！絲打加油！好多巴絲都係咁情況"},{"pid":"a72ba8074795d0574eeb0ec528f49df979ccc9ac","tid":1407400,"uid":223084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T16:09:42.000Z","msg":"同路人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0136d6f8595dc4def9a98a34fdc50c1375e9ba5c","tid":1407400,"uid":94456,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T16:10:12.000Z","msg":"我老母話元朗黑夜假既添啦，講極都唔聽"},{"pid":"3078b4a9723019d2934350778cb5983f1fdb41e1","tid":1407400,"uid":219784,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T16:13:12.000Z","msg":"由得佢講啦，反正佢都唔聽嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我老母係咁問白衫人依幾日做咩仲唔出嚟打示威者啦<br />\n我都冇眼睇了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a346fb173bf1f4b0078b4173872b9282d9d1eaf5","tid":1407400,"uid":295481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T16:15:43.000Z","msg":"8月5日，全民三罷！<br />\n<br />\n遍地開花 九巴不合作運動最後召集！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1406002\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1406002</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n所有最新資訊會係TG Group到發放，有意發夢參加的朋友請加入<br />\n<br />\n已有分區細group，入谷後pm admin<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/OmURXQ09pQAlcm8-nJTDLA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FOmURXQ09pQAlcm8-nJTDLA&d=wovbC19maxltJNBkbBY4lIICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=07d45978\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/OmURXQ09pQAlcm8-nJTDLA</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAFehx0H-9ZMmNP0guA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FAAAAAFehx0H-9ZMmNP0guA&d=wovbC19maxltJNBkbBY4lIICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=fc06e457\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAFehx0H-9ZMmNP0guA</a>"},{"pid":"22a9853708b66cf732114968df21b348979a55cc","tid":1407400,"uid":152222,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-0